.SS Installation Detection
.RS
.EX
if __cmd_exists $prog; then
  # Launch application
else
  __attempt_install_menus "$prog"
fi
.EE
.IP \(bu 2
Checks if application exists with __cmd_exists
.IP \(bu 2
Offers to install if missing
.IP \(bu 2
Uses zenity confirmation dialog
.IP \(bu 2
Proceeds with pkmgr silent install
.RE
.SS Installation Dialog
.RS
Zenity prompt when application missing:
.EX
"$prog is not installed!
Should I try to install it?"

[Yes] [No]
.EE
.IP \(bu 2
10-second timeout on installation prompt
.IP \(bu 2
Yes → proceed with pkmgr silent install
.IP \(bu 2
No → cancel and return to menu
.IP \(bu 2
Progress bar shown during installation
